title: Mickey.and.the.Roadster.Racers.S01E01-25.HDTV.x264-W4F
description:
Mickey and the Roadster Racers is about the Sensational Six (Mickey, Minnie, Goofy, Donald, Daisy, and Pluto) as they race around their town of Hot Dog Hills and around the world. Unlike the previous series, this show contains 2 11-minute stories as opposed to a full-length 22-minute story.

The second segment has Minnie and Daisy working as the Happy Helpers alongside Cuckoo-Loca (Who was introduced in the Minnie's Bow Toons shorts) where they help out different civilians of Hot Dog Hills. Minnie and Daisy utilize the Turnstyler in their office and the Happy Helper Van to assume the outfits associated with their jobs that they are hired to help out on
